Feature: Stories

  Background: Create a new Project
    Given I have set a connection to pivotal_tracker API service
    When I send a POST request to /projects with:
      |name|story7620|
      |public|true|
    Then I expect Status code 200
    And store as Project1

  @create_stories
  Scenario: Status code 200 when create new Stories on a Project
    Given I have set a connection to pivotal_tracker API service
    When I send a POST request to /projects/[Project1.id]/stories with:
      |name|newStories|
    Then I expect Status code 200